Catalog/model requirements:
- Normal wheel: forward/back along its local drive axis; a sideways normal wheel must not unlock all movement.
- Omni wheel: multi-axis/lateral capability.
- Mecanum wheel: diagonal/lateral behavior if catalog parts currently support it; otherwise document exact catalog blocker.
- Tank tread: forward/back with high traction if catalog parts currently support it; otherwise document exact catalog blocker.
- Fixed weapon: fire along local emitter axis.
- Turret/rotating part: capability direction uses explicit runtime rotation if current runtime state supports it; otherwise add minimal runtime orientation support or document exact blocker.

Must delete or quarantine from machine:v1 authority:
- deriveControls as the source of machine capabilities.
- BotBlueprint/BotDesignSnapshot projection as the source of machine capabilities.
- Any assumption that a wheel grants the full generic movement menu.
- Any assumption that a weapon fires forward unless its local emitter axis says so.

Forbidden shortcuts:
- Do not use storedDesignToLegacyBotBlueprintProjection or botDesignSnapshotToLegacyBotBlueprintProjection to derive machine capabilities.
- Do not use transform.rotation as a full basis unless this slice first makes that representation explicitly authoritative and tested.
